Learning, refining, reinventing. Each year, I try to improve my craft, learn from past mistakes, grow, and understand things a little more deeply. It’s not easy, but to me, it’s important. In that spirit, here’s a new reel featuring dear friends @keenanomeara @miameego singing ‘If I Could Leave’ 
Edit by @jessicapaige_ Happy Friday !

The next total solar eclipse is this Thursday, April 20, 2023 - viewable from Australia, Timor-Leste, and Indonesia. The next one in North America is April 8, 2024 - @tonycross and I are thinking Vermont would be a good place to see it. Your options are Mexico, Texas, Oklahoma, Arkansas, Missouri, Illinois, Kentucky, Indiana, Ohio, Pennsylvania, New York, Vermont, New Hampshire, Maine, Ontario, Quebec, New Brunswick, Prince Edward Island, and Cape Breton. This image was captured on August 21, 2017 and it was a very a magical day. Highly recommend if you can make it happen! Start planning and hope for clear skies 🙏
